OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,FMelania Trump has called on ABC to
OL,7,Ftake action over a sketch by comedian
OL,8,FJimmy Kimmel, which aired just days
OL,9,Fbefore the Washington hotel shooting,
OL,10,Fin which he described the First Lady
OL,11,Fas an "expectant widow".
OL,13,FShe described his rhetoric as "hateful
OL,14,Fand violent" and suggested his
OL,15,F"corrosive" routine only served to
OL,16,Fdeepen the "political sickness within
OL,17,FAmerica".
OL,19,FIn a parody of Saturday's White House
OL,20,FCorrespondents' dinner, Kimmel said:
OL,21,F"Our First Lady, Melania, is here.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777378266
OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,F"Look at Melania, so beautiful. Mrs
OL,7,FTrump, you have a glow like an
OL,8,Fexpectant widow... You know, Melania's
OL,9,Fbirthday in on Sunday.
OL,11,F"She's planning to celebrate at home
OL,12,Fthe same way she always does, looking
OL,13,Fout a window and whispering, 'What
OL,14,Fhave I done?'"
OL,16,FThe skit aired on Thursday, just two
OL,17,Fdays before a gunman opened fire at
OL,18,Fthe Washington Hilton, where an event
OL,19,Fwas being held to honour journalism
OL,20,Fand to raise money for scholarships.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
