OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777378266
OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump and his wife
OL,7,Fwere bundled to safety by Secret
OL,8,FService agents after shots were fired
OL,9,Fin the lobby of the hotel.
OL,11,FThe suspect, identified as teacher
OL,12,FCole Tomas Allen, 31, allegedly sent
OL,13,Fmessages to his family describing
OL,14,Fhimself as a "Friendly Federal
OL,15,FAssassin", and voiced grievances about
OL,16,Fthe actions of the US administration.
OL,18,FOne security officer, who was wearing
OL,19,Fa bulletproof vest, was hit, but is
OL,20,Fexpected to make a full recovery.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
