OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777378266
OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,FPosting on X on Monday, Melania Trump
OL,7,Fbroke her silence about Kimmel's
OL,8,Fremarks and suggested the network ABC
OL,9,Fwould protect the comedian.
OL,11,F"Kimmel's hateful and violent rhetoric
OL,12,Fis intended to divide our country,"
OL,13,Fshe wrote. "His monologue about my
OL,14,Ffamily isn't comedy- his words are
OL,15,Fcorrosive and deepens the political
OL,16,Fsickness within America.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777378266
OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,F"People like Kimmel shouldn't have the
OL,7,Fopportunity to enter our homes each
OL,8,Fevening to spread hate. A coward,
OL,9,FKimmel hides behind ABC because he
OL,10,Fknows the network will keep running
OL,11,Fcover to protect him.
OL,13,F"Enough is enough. It is time for ABC
OL,14,Fto take a stand. How many times will
OL,15,FABC's leadership enable Kimmel's
OL,16,Fatrocious behaviour at the expense of
OL,17,Four community."
OL,19,FABC is yet to comment on the backlash
OL,20,Fover Kimmel's sketch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
