OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis isn't the first time Kimmel has
OL,12,Ffaced controversy over jokes related
OL,13,Fto political violence in America.
OL,15,FIn September last year, the comedian
OL,16,Fwas briefly taken off air by ABC after
OL,17,Fsuggesting on his Jimmy Kimmel Live!
OL,18,Fshow that Donald Trump and his allies
OL,19,Fwere capitalising politically on the
OL,20,Fmurder of activist Charlie Kirk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
