PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1777378266
OL,3,CMelania Trump condemns 'hateful and
OL,4,Cviolent' skit by 'coward' Jimmy Kimmel
OL,6,FAfter returning to air after a near
OL,7,Fweeklong suspension, he told viewers:
OL,8,F"I have no illusions about changing
OL,9,Fanyone's mind, but I do want to make
OL,10,Fsomething clear, because it's
OL,11,Fimportant to me as a human.
OL,13,F"It was never my intention to make
OL,14,Flight of the murder of a young man. I
OL,15,Fdon't think there's anything funny
OL,16,Fabout it."
OL,18,FITV News has contacted ABC for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
